videos.description: South Carolina's Sindarius Thornwell energizes the Gamecocks' offense with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Thornwell sparks South Carolina's offense

videos.description: South Carolina's Sindarius Thornwell hits an open 3-pointer off great passing from the Gamecocks.
videos.headline: Thornwell hits open 3

videos.description: South Carolina's Duane Notice gets the steal and finishes with the one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Notice steals and scores

videos.description: Arkansas's Daryl Macon drains a 3-pointer with a hand in his face to help fire up the Razorbacks' offense.
videos.headline: Macon hits contested 3-pointer

videos.description: Arkansas's Dusty Hannahs and South Carolina's Duane Notice hit 3-pointers to stay competitive.
videos.headline: Arkansas and South Carolina trade 3s

videos.description: South Carolina's Sindarius Thornwell blocks Arkansas's Jaylen Barford, and Thornwell slams down the dunk.
videos.headline: Thornwell does it all with a block and mega-dunk

videos.description: South Carolina's Chris Silva makes the athletic alley-oop dunk off the lob from Hassani Gravett to electrify the Gamecocks' crowd.
videos.headline: Silva cracks down with thunderous alley-oop dunk

videos.description: South Carolina's Chris Silva finishes with a strong one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Silva takes out anger on the rim

videos.description: Arkansas coach Mike Anderson discusses his team's 83-76 win over No. 21 South Carolina.
videos.headline: Anderson: 'We're still in the hunt'
